<p>124.67 <b>Strengthen cooperation with human rights mechanisms and engage 
with OHCHR, and avail itself of the Office&#8217;s expertise, in order to demonstrate 
transparency and to adopt measures to better ensure the full enjoyment of 
human rights and fundamental freedoms for all (Sierra Leone); 
</b>124.68 <b>Observe the principle of non-discrimination and the international 
